description: MakyJames Grill is making its way through Boise and bringing out some great tasting American cuisine. With quality in every bite, this family-run truck’s selection of burgers, chicken sandwiches, wraps, salads, and fries are a total must-try. And for dessert? There is a delectable variety of fudge brownie sundaes, ice cream waffle boat sundaes, cakes, cobblers, pies, and so much more.The locals love all the delicious food from MakyJames Grill and you certainly will too.
name: MakyJames Grill
